text:
Visa, a world leader in digital payments, has appointed Emirates NBD as its official National Net Settlement Service (#NNSS) Agent in the UAE, allowing Visa’s domestic card transactions to be settled by Emirates NBD locally in UAE Dirhams (AED) in lieu of international settlement
